dct_title_s: Tunisia ; Advance of the Eighth Army
dct_description_sm: compiled and drawn in the Branch of Research and Analysis, OSS.
The map of Tunisia shows roads, railroads, and swamps. "Advance of the Eighth Army" covers the North African coast, from Beni Oulid to Suez, giving the date the Eighth Army arrived at each objective.
Relief on Tunisia map shown by shading.
